{"tid":2023953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廉署起訴油尖區女警 涉向證人攞折扣買波鞋耳環","createTime":"2020-05-19T10:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T10:40:22.000Z","uid":203615,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3c029c978b10ec56fa26c3ea6768bf04b1acb8","tid":2023953,"uid":203615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"廉政公署今日落案起訴一名女警，控告她涉嫌向警方調查的懷疑詐騙案件的相關人士，索取折扣以購買運動鞋，並接受以折扣價購買一對耳環。涉案的運動鞋據報在員工半價折扣後，價值2450元；而涉案的耳環據報低於市價2至3成，價值4500元。<br />\n<br />\n李倩華，29歲，女警，被控5項罪名，即4項公職人員索取利益及一項公職人員接受利益，均違反《防止賄賂條例》第4(2)(a)條；同案被告梁慧嘉，45歲，時裝公司前部門經理，及庄澳琳，31歲，珠寶公司前文員，各被控一項向公職人員提供利益罪名，違反《防止賄賂條例》第4(1)(a)條。各被告已獲廉署准予保釋，以待周四（21日）在西九龍裁判法院應訊。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，李倩華案發時為xxxx，駐守油尖區刑事一個調查隊，負責調查分派給該隊的案件；<br />\n梁慧嘉為一間時裝公司的部門經理，她可以員工折扣購買公司指定產品；庄澳琳則是一間珠寶公司的文員，她能物色低於市價的珠寶產品.......<br />\n<br />\nsource :<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200519/SBKUKJQTOPJ7OX7LOXHJE3MEWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200519%2FSBKUKJQTOPJ7OX7LOXHJE3MEWQ%2F&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=d46cbe2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200519%2FSBKUKJQTOPJ7OX7LOXHJE3MEWQ%2F&h=87cd3eef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200519/SBKUKJQTOPJ7OX7LOXHJE3MEWQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3357760fd3af1c939fc6a9646d7268a031bc6507","tid":2023953,"uid":101945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:29:58.000Z","msg":"又拉散仔 幫黑驚降溫 <br />\n冇人會原諒 都係祝死全家啦"},{"pid":"312e466c3ec93cb30d14cabb79b54b5c795105d6","tid":2023953,"uid":203615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/